&lt;p&gt;Selenium includes findElement functions, like so... &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;.find_element_by_&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-py s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-python&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-built_in&quot;&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;
